divs: sighting detailsi was practicing some amateur astrophotography with a canon powershot a560, 6 second exposure, iso 200. during previous shots i noticed a few satellite\airplane type points of light moving across the sky. after taking the photo, it was during review on the computer i noticed the strange object that appeared and the end of the light trail. i am by no means a photo analyser, i would think that the object at the end of the light trail should appeared "streaked" similar to the trail. look at the end of the "trail" just above and to the left of the window. attached is the unaltered, original photo.
